<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT39">
<l>aḻaippaṉ tiruvēṅ kaṭattāṉaik kāṇa</l>
<l>viḻaippaṉ tirukkūṭal kūṭa maḻaippē</l>
<l>raruvi maṇivaraṉṟi vantiḻiya yāṉai</l>
<l>veruvi yaravoṭuṅkum veṟpu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will call the Lord of sacred Vēṅkaṭam in order to see [Him]!</l>
<l>I will draw the sacred kūṭal-circle so as to rejoin the mountain</l>
<l>where the elephants are startled and the snakes hide themselves</l>
<l>As the big waterfalls come descending, gathering gems during the rainy season.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
